# Privacy Policy

**Effective Date:** February 16, 2026

## 1. Introduction
This Privacy Policy explains how **Ã‡engel Master** handles your information when you use our mobile application. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring you understand that your data remains yours.

## 2. Information We Collect
**We do not collect, store, or share any personal information on our servers.**

### 2.1. Game Data
All game progress, puzzle completions, diamond balances, and settings are stored locally on your device. We do not upload or sync your game data to any external server.

### 2.2. Usage Data
We do not collect personal usage data. Any crash reports or performance metrics are collected anonymously by Apple (if you have opted in to share analytics with developers) and do not contain personally identifiable information.

## 3. Third-Party Services
We use trusted third-party services to facilitate app functionality:

### 3.1. RevenueCat
We use **RevenueCat** to manage subscriptions and in-app purchases.
*   RevenueCat manages the validation of your subscription receipt from Apple.
*   They may process an anonymous App User ID to track subscription status.
*   No personal data (such as your name or email) is shared with RevenueCat.
*   [RevenueCat Privacy Policy](https://www.revenuecat.com/privacy)

### 3.2. Google AdMob
We use **Google AdMob** to display advertisements in the app.
*   AdMob may collect device identifiers and usage data to serve relevant ads.
*   If you have opted out of personalized ads, only non-personalized ads will be shown.
*   No personal data is shared with AdMob by our app directly.
*   [Google Privacy Policy](https://policies.google.com/privacy)

## 4. In-App Purchases & Subscriptions
Subscriptions, in-app purchases, and payments are processed directly by the **Apple App Store**. We do not have access to your credit card information or billing details.

## 5. Children's Privacy
Our app does not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13. The app does not require any personal information to function.

## 6. Security
Because we do not collect your personal data, your information is inherently secure. All game data remains on your device unless you explicitly choose to delete the app.

## 7. Updates to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. If we make material changes, we will notify you through the app or by updating the date at the top of this policy.

## 8. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
*   **Email:** bartuyesilbag@gmail.com
